":null,"search-option":null},"Phasmophobia"],"in VR. We had a PSVR1 back in the day and the family really liked it. I bet this one will be a hit too.\n"],["paragraph",null,["link",{"type":"id","type-explicit-p":true,"path":"0DC930ED-C578-4437-BB19-343436415CCE","format":"bracket","raw-link":"id:0DC930ED-C578-4437-BB19-343436415CCE","application":null,"search-option":null},"I"],"have been working on ",["link",{"type":"id","type-explicit-p":true,"path":"58233C2C-F23C-4CB1-8660-D9FAB87A5E0D","format":"bracket","raw-link":"id:58233C2C-F23C-4CB1-8660-D9FAB87A5E0D","application":null,"search-option":null},"prototyping a redesign of my website"],"that uses my org-roam database as content served from an SSR rust backend. It has been so fun to see this idea slowly come to life. \n"],["paragraph",null,["link",{"type":"id","type-explicit-p":true,"path":"0DC930ED-C578-4437-BB19-343436415CCE","format":"bracket","raw-link":"id:0DC930ED-C578-4437-BB19-343436415CCE","application":null,"search-option":null},"I"],"made a mistake on the work to ",["link",{"type":"id","type-explicit-p":true,"path":"BF18B0C9-8920-4166-9071-4560D3D22EF0","format":"bracket","raw-link":"id:BF18B0C9-8920-4166-9071-4560D3D22EF0","application":null,"search-option":null},"Add world: MAIN to Firefox FIDO2 Registration"],". This change broke passkeys on Firefox. ",["link",{"type":"id","type-explicit-p":true,"path":"59d43593-8318-4af9-a799-f9b440cf0314","format":"bracket","raw-link":"id:59d43593-8318-4af9-a799-f9b440cf0314","application":null,"search-option":null},"Andreas Coroiu"],"fixed it for me over the holiday. ",["link",{"type":"id","type-explicit-p":true,"path":"0DC930ED-C578-4437-BB19-343436415CCE","format":"bracket","raw-link":"id:0DC930ED-C578-4437-BB19-343436415CCE","application":null,"search-option":null},"I"],"'m very grateful.\n"],["paragraph",null,["link",{"type":"id","type-explicit-p":true,"path":"9F4B874E-2973-460E-8CBF-64A85358F9F1","format":"bracket","raw-link":"id:9F4B874E-2973-460E-8CBF-64A85